com.rbmhtechnology.vind.api.query.filter

Class Filter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rbmhtechnology.vind.api.query.filter.Filter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Filter.AfterFilter, Filter.AndFilter, Filter.BeforeFilter, Filter.BetweenDatesFilter, Filter.BetweenNumericFilter, Filter.ChildrenDocumentFilter, Filter.DescriptorFilter, Filter.GreaterThanFilter, Filter.LowerThanFilter, Filter.NotEmptyFilter, Filter.NotEmptyLocationFilter, Filter.NotEmptyTextFilter, Filter.NotFilter, Filter.OrFilter, Filter.PrefixFilter, Filter.TermFilter, Filter.WithinBBoxFilter, Filter.WithinCircleFilter

    public abstract class Filter
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class to be implemented by filter query objects (Filter.AndFilter, Filter.OrFilter, Filter.NotFilter, Filter.TermFilter, Filter.DescriptorFilter, Filter.BetweenDatesFilter, Filter.BeforeFilter, Filter.AfterFilter, Filter.BetweenNumericFilter, Filter.GreaterThanFilter, Filter.LowerThanFilter) and providing static user friendly methods to create them.
